# STM32 Build Artifacts (Firmware)
firmware/**/Debug/
firmware/**/Release/
firmware/**/.metadata/

# KiCad Auto-Backups (Electronics)
electronics/**/*-backups/
electronics/**/*.bak
electronics/**/*.bck

# SolidWorks Temporary Lock Files (Mechanical)
mechanical/**/~$*.sldprt
mechanical/**/~$*.sldasm
mechanical/**/~$*.slddrw